OL,3,CRacist abuse of Romeo & Juliet theatre
OL,4,Cstar condemned by production company
OL,6,FRomeo And Juliet will run at the Duke
OL,7,FOf York's Theatre from Saturday May 11
OL,8,Fto Saturday August 3
OL,10,FRacist comments aimed at a cast member
OL,11,Fof a new production of Romeo and
OL,12,FJuliet starring Tom Holland have been
OL,13,Fcondemned as "deplorable" by a company.
OL,15,FThe Jamie Lloyd Company said the abuse
OL,16,Ftowards an unnamed cast member "must
OL,17,Fstop" and that it is continuing to
OL,18,F"support and protect everyone in our
OL,19,Fcompany at all costs".
