OL,6,FThe development comes after the full
OL,7,Fcast of the show was announced last
OL,8,Fmonth, with Francesca Amewudah-Rivers
OL,9,Fto star as Juliet alongside Holland -
OL,10,Fwho will play Romeo.
OL,12,FTomiwa Edun, Freema Agyeman and Joshua
OL,13,FAlexander-Williams are among the other
OL,14,Fcastings that have been announced -
OL,15,Freprising the roles of Capulet, Nurse
OL,16,Fand Mercutio respectively.
