OL,3,CRacist abuse of Romeo & Juliet theatre
OL,4,Cstar condemned by production company
OL,6,FIn a statement, The Jamie Lloyd
OL,7,FCompany said: "Following the
OL,8,Fannouncement of our Romeo & Juliet
OL,9,Fcast, there has been a barrage of
OL,10,Fdeplorable racial abuse online
OL,11,Fdirected towards a member of our
OL,12,Fcompany.
OL,14,F"This must stop. We are working with a
OL,15,Fremarkable group of artists. We insist
OL,16,Fthat they are free to create work
OL,17,Fwithout facing online harassment."
