OL,6,FThe statement added "bullying and
OL,7,Fharassment have no place online, in
OL,8,Four industry or in our wider
OL,9,Fcommunities" and that rehearsals will
OL,10,Fcontinue with "generosity and love,
OL,11,Fand focus on the creation of our
OL,12,Fproduction".
OL,14,FHolland's return to the theatre stage
OL,15,Frepresents his first major role since
OL,16,Fhis debut in Billy Elliot The Musical
OL,17,Fin 2008.
